---
import { MapPin, Home, Utensils, HeartHandshake } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="about" class="py-28 bg-white px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-emerald-50/40 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-stone-50 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column: Story & Description -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
        <span class="text-emerald-700 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-xs font-bold block">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-900 leading-tight">
          A Serene Sanctuary At the Foothills of Shillong Peak
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
          Romillie Hadeljo is a peaceful guest house located at Lumpyngngad, nestled at the foothills of the majestic Shillong Peak. Situated close to a lush forest reserve, it offers the ultimate quiet escape from busy city life while remaining remarkably accessible via Motinagar Road.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
          Enjoy sweeping, panoramic views of the Shillong skyline and nature's quiet rustle right at your doorstep. We are located just 2 km from Laitumkhrah and 5 km from Police Bazar, giving you the perfect balance of peaceful seclusion and city convenience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Highlight Grid -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Homely Accommodation -->
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-3.5 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-colors">
            <Home className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-800" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-3">Homely Accommodation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
            Five beautifully furnished rooms with attached bathrooms. Select rooms offer private balconies or terraces with hillside views. Enjoy our shared living room and cozy lounge area designed to make your stay pleasant and memorable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Attentive Service -->
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-3.5 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-colors">
            <HeartHandshake className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-800" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-3">Attentive Hospitality</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
            Experience authentic warmth. Our manager-cum-housekeeper resides in the same building, ready to serve, assist, and attend to your needs whenever required.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Dining & Homemade Meals -->
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-3.5 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-colors">
            <Utensils className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-800" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-3">Dining Options</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
            Start your morning with a healthy, delicious breakfast. For other meals, request homemade preparations by our onsite cook, order food online, or explore fine dining restaurants located just a few minutes away.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Perfect Location -->
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-3.5 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-colors">
            <MapPin className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-800" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-3">Conveniently Accessible</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
            Easily approachable via Motinagar Road. We are situated close to a peaceful forest reserve, yet only 2 km from Laitumkhrah and 5 km from Police Bazar, making transit and shopping seamless.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
